article.description: — Cam Mack had 15 points and six assists as Prairie View defeated Grambling State 59-50 on Monday night.
article.headline: Mack leads Prairie View past Grambling St. 59-50
article.linkText: Mack leads Prairie View past Grambling St. 59-50
article.story: PRAIRIE VIEW, Texas -- — Cam Mack had 15 points and six assists as Prairie View defeated Grambling State 59-50 on Monday night. Jawaun Daniels had 11 points and nine rebounds for Prairie View (3-4, 2-0 Southwestern Athletic Conference). DeWayne Cox added nine rebounds and Jerroda Briscoe had four blocks. Trevell Cunningham had 12 points for the Tigers (5-7, 3-2). Cameron Christon added 11 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
